<br>
One thing I didn't like, the game feels like EQ, but I found the realms rather badly made.  Basically, everyone starts near the same place so you can't go far in you're realm as you will die, the realms are divided in sections aimed by levels and whenever I went for a walk, I saw just about no one.  So that meant that everyone did the same quests, fought the same mobs, and everything was the same, so I got bored very quickly...  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9>OT/OOC Forum</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href="http://www.firionavie.org/">Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.6.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  